 </row> 
 <row>
  <entry namest="c1" nameend="c2">Since the left side is the variable side, the 6 is out of place. We must "undo" adding 6 by subtracting 6, and to keep the equality we must subtract 6 from both sides. Use the Subtraction Property of Equality.</entry>
   <entry><media id="eip-id1168468595447" alt="."><image mime-type="image/jpeg" src="../../media/CNX_BMath_Figure_08_03_039_img-02.png"/></media></entry>
 </row>  
<row>
