 </row> 
 <row>
   <entry>Combine like terms.</entry>
   <entry><media id="eip-id1168468567044" alt="."><image mime-type="image/jpeg" src="../../media/CNX_BMath_Figure_08_03_035_img-03.png"/></media></entry>
 </row>
 <row>
   <entry>Add 2 to both sides to collect constants on the right.</entry>
   <entry><media id="eip-id1168468567060" alt="."><image mime-type="image/jpeg" src="../../media/CNX_BMath_Figure_08_03_035_img-04.png"/></media></entry>
